h School (Midland, Texas)">Midland Lee</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Midland_High_School_(Midland,_Texas)" title="Midland High School (Midland, Texas)">Midland High</a> – which lost the toss. This was the 1988 season, and the three schools had identical 5–1 <i>district</i> records; overall records differed.</span></li>
